'''阿扎姆·巴拉卡'''（{{lang-en|Ajamu Baraka}}；{{bd|1953年|10月25日|}}<ref name="Quanki">{{cite web|title=Ajamu S Baraka|url=http://quanki.com/person.php?person=06ESTHVAB98|website=Quanki|accessdate=20 September 2016|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223220329/http://quanki.com/person.php?person=06ESTHVAB98|dead-url=no}}</ref>），是一名[[非裔美国人|非裔美国]][[人权|人权]]運動家，在[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]中由[[吉爾·斯泰因|吉爾·斯泰因]]提名為[[美國綠黨|美國綠黨]][[美国副总统|副总统]]候選人<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jill2016.com/jill_stein_selects_ajamu_baraka_as_running_mate|title=Jill Stein Selects Human Rights Activist Ajamu Baraka as Vice-Presidential Running Mate|date=August 1, 2016|accessdate=August 1, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013114103/http://www.jill2016.com/jill_stein_selects_ajamu_baraka_as_running_mate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他和斯泰因通過2016年8月6日的{{le|2016年綠黨全國代表大會|2016 Green National Convention|綠黨全國代表大會}}中正式得到提名<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nelson|first1=Eliot|title=The Green Party Picks Its Presidential Ticket|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/green-party-presidential-ticket_us_57a64585e4b03ba680128f32|website=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=August 6, 2016|date=August 6, 2016|archive-date=2017-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107180408/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/green-party-presidential-ticket_us_57a64585e4b03ba680128f32|dead-url=no}}</ref>，巴拉卡在其提名演講指出加入綠黨是為了「在勞動人民的需求和願望的基礎上在這個國家建立一個跨國運動」（"build a multinational movement here in this country based on the needs and the aspirations of working people"）<ref>{{cite web|title=A New Day & Another Way: Green VP Nominee Ajamu Baraka Urges Progressives to Reject Two-Party System|url=http://www.democracynow.org/2016/8/8/a_new_day_another_way_green|website=[[Democracy_Now|Democracy Now]]|accessdate=August 9, 2016|date=August 8, 2016|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314180706/https://www.democracynow.org/2016/8/8/a_new_day_another_way_green|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

